content.rendered:
Directed by Milan Luthria

Written by Rajat Arora. Ajay Bhupathi

Star Ahan Shetty (Ishana). Tara Sutaria (Ramisa). Saurabh Shukla (Daddy). Kumud Mishra (Nautiyal). Sumit Gulati (Lol). Mangala Kenkre (Dadi (as Mangal Kenkare)). Sourav Chakraborty (Guthli (as Saurav Chakrabarti)). Rajesh Khera (Negi). Hashim Haider (Kashi). Sohaila Kapur (Cafe Lady). Brij Bhushan Shukla (Bhandari). Sharik Ahmed (Mahesh). Mayank Tewari (Local Man 1 (as Mayank Tiwari)). Manoj Kukshal (Local Man 2). Geeta Ram Sharma (Jiyaram). Amin Lakhani (Coal Mine Manager). Bhanu Joshi (House Helper)

Language Hindi

Producers Amit Gupta. Dipti Jindal. Milan Luthria. Sajid Nadiadwala. Anup Pathade. Abinash Rout. Rohit Sangwan. Mayank Tiwari

Production Fox STAR Studios. Nadiadwala Grandson Entertainment
